data.title: Friday 20th September: Kevin & Perry Go Large in Portsmouth at The Gaiety Southsea, South Parade Pier
data.meta_description: Expected to see out quickly! 18+. Photo ID must be shown upon entry.
data.text:
Field Events Presents...

"COME ON!"... it's BACK... after 5 amazing SOLD OUT events in Portsmouth.

Kevin & Perry Go Large in Portsmouth

Friday 20th September 2024 7.30pm - 12.00am

FEAT. KEVIN & PERRY DJ SET

Official! Viral sensation to millions and millions, touring the world!

DJ EYEBALL PAUL

Superstar DJ! IBIZA DANCE, TRANCE ANTHEMS & 90s / 00s Hits

FILM PLAYLIST + FILM PLAYED ON LARGE SCREENS + LASER LIGHTS + GLOW STICKS

Dance to tracks from the film - expect one brilliant and HUGE party atmosphere!

FANCY DRESS (OPTIONAL)

"One of the best nights out I have had in years!"

"Just brilliant!"

"Please bring this back again, we had so much fun!"

"Danced from start to finish. Superb!"

Messages from the last event at The Gaiety Southsea!

The film will be played back on large screens!

"If I wasn't so much older and wider I'd swear this was me. Lovely stuff!" - Kathy Burke (who played Perry)

Last set finishes 12.00am. *All the above is subject to change. Please note, no actors from the film will be present.

10% booking fees apply. Strictly 18+. ID may be required.

If for any reason the event is cancelled your tickets will be refunded excluding the booking fee. See https://book.events/terms
